  "remarks": "QDi.062\nTunisian national identity number W374031, issued on 11 April 2011.\nProfessor of Chemistry. Deported from Italy to Tunisia on 27 Aug. 2006. Legally changed family name from Aouani to Lakhal in 2014. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 22 Apr. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 24 April 2002 (amended 26 Nov. 2004 and 9 Sep. 2005, 31 Jul. 2006, 23 Dec. 2010 and 24 Nov 2014, 6 Dec 2019, 7 May 2020, 30 Oct. 2023).",
